        "subject": "LU-8982 ldlm: limit recovery timer to allow VBR",
        "message": "LU-8982 ldlm: limit recovery timer to allow VBR\n\nWhen one client reconnected to server, the recovery timer will\nbe checked and restarted if the timeout contained in the client\nconnection request, the timer should not exceed hard recovery\ntimeout, VBR will not be processed otherwise\n\nChange-Id: If97912400b9528e288d1c8253a35d148061d110e\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\n"
